		"txt":"[{\"instruction\":\"It is suitable for large-scale online transaction scenarios of E-commerce and O2O. It enables warehouse and table sorting for user, order, commodity, logistics and other data, and supports mass transactions with high concurrency. Moreover, it is also easy for horizontal expansion of database, and can improve the concurrency capacity, processing capacity and storage capacity of the whole system.\",\"name\":\"E-commerce and O2O Online Transaction\",\"picUrl\":\"//img1.jcloudcs.com/cms/0824e0f3-64ef-44a5-b4dd-0c1823a0858020180706175309.png\",\"selectedProduct\":[],\"buttons\":{\"name\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"classTag\":\"\"}},{\"instruction\":\"Strong sub-warehouse and sub-table capacity supports automatic data fragmentation and can store data onto the backend MySQL node by the given fragmentation policy and expand by need at any time. It is suitable for fragmental search and analysis of mass data (for instance, time-based historical information search) and summary of regional data.\",\"name\":\"Fragmental Search and Analysis of Mass Data\",\"picUrl\":\"//img1.jcloudcs.com/cms/6c76af8f-f14c-47f3-8f90-6a280d14238620180706175349.png\",\"selectedProduct\":[],\"buttons\":{\"name\":\"\",\"link\":\"\",\"classTag\":\"\"}}]",
